{"type":null,"faqId":45355,"title":"荣耀盒子M321在电视画面上显示不够清晰怎么办？","answer":"<p>\"1. 盒子分辨率过低。请进入“设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; HDMI 分辨率”，设置为1080P 或 4K（该处显示电视机支持的分辨率，比如部分电视机不支持4K， 4K 选项将不会显示）。 <br>\n2. 进入盒子“设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; 视频质量”，选择“开启”，画面会更清晰。<br>\n3. 电视机的分辨率设置过低。请参考电视机的说明书调高电视机的分辨率。<br>\n4. 调高片源的清晰度。盒子播放在线片源时，按遥控器菜单键，选择更高清晰度。<br>\n部分电视机或视频本身为非高清，此时画面不够清晰，属于正常现象。\" <br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":247,"faqType":"显示","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"876","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556876000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":32,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"显示,不清晰,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}